Package: fastFoodStats
Title: Fast Food Nutrition Analysis Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Luis", "Rivera", email = "lriveralozano@usf.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A simple R package for analyzing and comparing nutrition data from popular fast food restaurants. It allows users to explore calories, protein, sugar, fat, and sodium across different menu items.
